				<h2>
					Programming Skills</h2>
				<h2>
					Wittawat Keawcharoen</h2>
				<h4>
					Programming Languages</h4>
				<p>
					I use C/C++ on my everyday work and I&#39;m personally try to keep myself up to date with the new standard C++0X. I usually use C# on Tools, Quick Prototypes and Personal projects. I am also familiar with scripting languages which are used in our in-house tools such as Lua and Python.</p>
				<p>
					Related APIs: STL, Boost</p>
				<h4>
					GPU Programming</h4>
				<p>
					I frequently use HLSL and Cg in my everyday work. GLSL has been used from time to time for Prototyping Mobile/Web games.&nbsp;I also try to experiment and learn some GPGPU languages such as DirectCompute and CUDA on my personal interests</p>
				<p>
					I&#39;ve used FXComposer for experimenting new shaders, and sometimes for a quick prototyping.&nbsp;</p>
