				<h4>
					Multi-Platform Development</h4>
				<p>
					I am highly familiar with the Multi-platform development and have experienced working on most of the modern consoles, XBOX360/Kinect, PS3 and PC Direct3D 9/10. Currently I&rsquo;m accelerating myself into DirectX 11, spending my day-to-day experimenting with their new features and rendering pipeline, preparing for the next-gens.</p>
				<p>
					I use OpenGL on some of my personal projects and I also have good knowledge on some previous gens consoles such as, PS2 and GBA.</p>
