					Profilers</h4>
				<p>
					I work and very well familiar with these profiling tools such as PIX, GPAD, NVPerf API, Intel GPA and Intel VTune Analyser. I use them in my everyday work, mostly for debugging and measuring GPU performance.</p>
				<h4>
					PC Developments/Game Engines</h4>
				<p>
					PC is my main learning tools, where I use it to explore new techniques, interesting APIs, create my personal projects and develop some tools. For some game prototyping, I use Unity with Kinect, OGRE3D, SlimDX, OpenTK and XNA. I am also quite well familiar with CryEngine(Dunia). &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>
