					I strongly believe that Video Game is the creation of Arts, and all sorts of creative activities are somehow connected. This is the reason why I&rsquo;m interested in all other type of creativities as well. I am a Guitar player, and I can create my own Music. I am also interested in Fine arts, Modern arts, Japanese stuffs, cooking, Drawing, Manga and etc.</div>
