				<h3 style="margin-top: 1em;">
					Research Projects</h3>
				<p>
					<em>Oct 2008-May 2009</em>: <strong>&ldquo;Rendering of a Massive number of Objects&rdquo;, University of Abertay Dundee, UK.</strong><br />
					The research has been carried on during my Honours year. The research addresses an interesting problem in modern game applications regarding to real-time rendering, where a game scene is detailed with large number of various kinds of objects.<br />
					<br />
					Continue to read the full article in <a href="http://my-site:5000/cms/joomla17//cms/joomla17/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=61&amp;catid=7&amp;Itemid=121" title="Character Instancing (2009)">Character Instancing (2009)</a><br />
